      <bioghist id="aspace_9323a66304447321c176177e8b052132">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Facilities Development and Operations Department is responsible for space planning, renovation and new construction, daily maintenance and cleaning, and asset management at the Yale School of Medicine</p>  
